<%- include('../partials/legal-layout', {
  legalTitle: 'Shipping Policy',
  legalBody: `
    <p class="text-[0.95rem] text-ink-3">For full delivery windows, packaging detail, and process timeline see <a class="link-underline" href="/shipping">/shipping</a>.</p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Fulfilment origin</h2>
    <p>All orders are picked, packed, and dispatched from our fulfilment hub inside the European Union. Shipments to EU member states are not subject to customs duties or import taxes. Shipments to the United Kingdom, Switzerland, Norway, Iceland, and the rest of the world clear customs with accurate declarations as research-use laboratory chemicals.</p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Delivery windows</h2>
    <p><strong>EU Priority</strong> (DE · AT · NL · BE · LU · CZ · DK): 2\u20133 business days standard, 1\u20132 business days express.</p>
    <p><strong>EU Standard</strong> (FR · IT · ES · PT · PL · HU · SK · SI · HR · IE): 3\u20135 business days standard, 2\u20133 business days express.</p>
    <p><strong>EU & Nordics</strong> (SE · FI · EE · LV · LT · RO · BG · GR · MT · CY): 4\u20137 business days.</p>
    <p><strong>UK / Switzerland / Norway / Iceland</strong>: 4\u20137 business days, customs paperwork prepared.</p>
    <p><strong>International (rest of world)</strong>: 7\u201314 business days standard, 5\u20138 business days express.</p>
    <p>All quoted windows are estimates; carrier delays and customs clearance are outside our control once a shipment has been handed over.</p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Free shipping threshold</h2>
    <p>Orders of $250 or more (subtotal, before shipping) qualify for free EU Standard shipping. Free shipping does not apply to express upgrades or to non-EU destinations.</p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Discreet packaging</h2>
    <p>Every parcel ships in plain, unmarked outer packaging. No product names, brand marks, chemical references, or hazard labels appear on the exterior. The return address uses a generic fulfilment-partner identifier rather than a brand or company name. Vials are individually wrapped, shock-protected, and labelled with batch and lot only \u2014 the COA is verified by lot number on the order page after dispatch.</p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Cold-chain handling</h2>
    <p>All shipments use insulated EPS mailers with phase-change cooling inserts that maintain transit temperature for up to 96 hours. Lyophilised peptides are stable at room temperature for the standard transit window; the cold-chain mailer is an additional safety margin against carrier delays.</p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Order processing</h2>
    <p>Orders confirmed on-chain before 14:00 CET on a working day are dispatched the same business day. Weekend or public-holiday confirmations dispatch the next working day. A tracking number is emailed at the moment of carrier handover.</p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Address accuracy & re-shipment</h2>
    <p>You are responsible for providing a complete and accurate shipping address. Parcels returned to us due to incorrect or insufficient addresses are re-shipped at cost. We are not liable for delivery failures attributable to incorrect address details, missed deliveries, or carrier-side delays after dispatch.</p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Recipient responsibilities</h2>
    <p>It is the recipient\u2019s responsibility to ensure that the import and possession of research peptides is permitted in their jurisdiction. Customs duties, import taxes, or local fees (where applicable) are payable by the recipient. Some destinations may be restricted by carrier policy or local regulation \u2014 we will notify you at order placement if your destination cannot be served.</p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Restrictions</h2>
    <p>We do not ship to PO boxes for cold-chain orders. Pre-mixed or temperature-sensitive products may have additional regional restrictions, which will be flagged at checkout.</p>
  `
}) %>
